like that before.

319
00:40:20,091 --> 00:40:24,073
Police are all power freaks.
He's just warped.

320
00:40:24,596 --> 00:40:27,907
Maybe he was a stool-pigeon.
He has a sly face.

321
00:40:28,333 --> 00:40:29,243
Idiot!

322
00:40:30,668 --> 00:40:32,113
