00:44:51,029 --> 00:44:54,647
You're a fool, Momo!
You got the wrong idea!

359
00:44:54,699 --> 00:44:56,576
Pipe down!

360
00:44:57,902 --> 00:45:01,406
Because of me and Midori here,
