if you have to.

391
00:50:43,314 --> 00:50:46,375
You're a shrew.
He'll be good for you.

392
00:50:47,251 --> 00:50:51,643
I had the wrong idea, Brother.

393
00:50:53,124 --> 00:50:55,946
