394
00:51:00,965 --> 00:51:02,649
You're a fool.

395
00:53:00,985 --> 00:53:02,123
I'm thirsty.

396
00:53:02,419 --> 00:53:05,229
Let's get dressed
and get some beer.

397
00:53:11,795 --> 00:53:14,765
Hello, little girl,
