a very nice girl.

507
01:04:38,148 --> 01:04:39,274
Go to her.

508
01:04:41,651 --> 01:04:42,800
Go to Okyo.

509
01:05:19,623 --> 01:05:20,738
Good luck!

510
01:05:23,493 --> 01:05:26,099
