515
01:07:28,385 --> 01:07:31,082
Hey, boys, he gave us a tip.

516
01:07:35,058 --> 01:07:36,981
Let's thank him.

517
01:07:39,462 --> 01:07:40,987
Fall in!

518
01:07:41,631 --> 01:07:43,668
