519
01:08:05,655 --> 01:08:07,612
Thanks,
That was a great help.

520
01:08:08,792 --> 01:08:10,180
Shall I wait?

521
01:08:11,895 --> 01:08:14,842
You don't have to.
I'll take a train.

522
01:08:14,931 --> 01:08:15,944
